      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"ToyCarCompositing-Compositing\">Compositing</h3><p>This project marked my first experience with node-based compositing in Nuke.</p><p /><p>To keep the pipeline consistent, I worked within an ACES color workflow, configuring OCIO in Nuke to convert sRGB footage into ACESCG.</p><p>I combined AOVs using shuffle nodes and used Cryptomatte to isolate specific surfaces where I enhanced or reduced reflections based on lighting and composition.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image13.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image13.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694121&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=328\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/654868513/image13.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694121&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"437\" data-width=\"1010\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"654671945\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image13.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"654868513\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"65f722ac-b5b2-4a58-be95-126d6d4a2ca6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image13.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694121&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1346&amp;height=582 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image13.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694121&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=328 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image10.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=268\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/654868513/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"465\" data-width=\"1315\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"654671952\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image10.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"654868513\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"33e397fa-ed3c-43dd-afea-bf5497f278de\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1315&amp;height=465 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=268 1x\"></span><p /><p>Some background elements required manual rotoscoping to separate them cleanly. For the breakdown, I also included UVs, wireframes, and checkerboard overlays. The TV screen, which I modeled and rendered separately, was composited directly into the final shot in Nuke.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image7.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image7.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694235&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=667\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/654868513/image7.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694235&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1061\" data-width=\"1208\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"654671958\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image7.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"654868513\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f6902291-642a-4369-84c7-ccb7a39eb889\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image7.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694235&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1208&amp;height=1061 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image7.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694235&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=667 1x\"></span><p /><p>... and here we have the final image!</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image5.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/654868513/image5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1125\" data-width=\"1999\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"654671964\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image5.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"654868513\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"248f05d3-2e28-4968-a7b9-79163d29c7a5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/654868513/image5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504694268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>This project was a personal journey for me. Don’t forget to download the project and take a closer look. I hope you enjoy it as much as I did. </p><p>Have fun!</p><p />"
